OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy overnight with showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain slowly clearing
OL,8,Fsouthwards during the night. Rather
OL,9,Fbreezy, particularly near Bristol
OL,10,FChannel coasts. Turning chilly in the
OL,11,Fnorth under clear spells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAfter a chilly and cloudy
OL,14,Fstart, there will be plenty of dry and
OL,15,Fbright weather around by Sunday
OL,16,Fafternoon. Feeling cooler with
OL,17,Ftemperatures below average for early
OL,18,Fto mid-May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
